        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只为打牙恨，时刻挂在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大战江南一十一，刀兵滚滚乱华夷。不是琼五来救驾，本藩焉能回故里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本藩唐国公李渊。只因解粮汉子辕门发笑，怒恼老大王，问他个惊驾之罪，推"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "出斩首。是我将他保留下来，发在慎法司命俺审问。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左右，打道慎法司！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将那解粮汉子带上堂来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦琼 （内西皮导板） 喝令一声要斩首！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦琼上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苍天哪，苍天！想俺秦琼来在边廷，怎比公衙行事。只为辕门发笑一声，老大"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王问俺个惊驾之罪，推出斩首。也不知哪位令公王侯保留下来。此番进帐谢过"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "救命之恩，回至家中高堂奉母也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "险些去了项上头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汗马功劳不到头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命中无有莫强求。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "烦恼言语惹祸由。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本官差我下登州。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王一怒要斩人头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因此才把活命留。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见了千岁把恩酬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人秦琼，叩谢千岁救命之恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自从三皇五帝后"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命中若有终须有"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是非只为多开口"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八旬老母家等候"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因辕门发笑吼"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多亏恩官来保奏"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔宝撩衣大帐走"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦琼！辕门发笑，莫非笑老大王用兵不当么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人怎敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "笑从何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人笑瓦岗罗成，不知进退。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那罗成乃将门之子，公卿之后，难道他不如你？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人看来，他实实不如小人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是甚等出身？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人在历城县，当了一名捕盗快手。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！既当快手，出身不高，赶出帐去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喝令一声赶出帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "羞的豪杰脸无光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想起当年事两桩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！适才千岁说我出身不高，想我虽当快手，也见过大小战场。不免进帐把"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "话言明，纵死九泉，瞑目甘心也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鹦鹉架上凤难招，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沙滩无水怎藏蛟？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猫儿食怎喂金钱豹？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "玉麒麟岂与犬同槽？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见了千岁说根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦琼二次叩见千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "低下头来心思想"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔宝二次宝帐到"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二次进帐莫非不怕死么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启千岁：蝼蚁尚且贪生，为人岂不惜命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何话讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人方才说了捕盗快手，千岁说小人出身不高；小人虽当快手，也见过大小战"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，本藩最喜的战场。将你大战场压下，小战场讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回禀千岁：小人乃是行伍出身，说到热闹中间有些比手划脚，又恐惊驾不便，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "求千岁松了小人的堂规。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本藩也是行伍出身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，松了他的堂规。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年小英雄志，习武并习文。文武俱习会，货与帝王君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掌中无刀怎杀人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打罢春夏又交秋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扭项回头观王侯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "流落公衙有数秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启千岁：想我历城县乃是九省要道，那年有位皇甫大人，去往天堂潞州荣任，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "路过历城，彼时我家太爷带领人役等接进公馆。酒席筵前，皇甫大人问到我家"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太爷，此去天堂潞州，一路之上可有阻隔无有？我家太爷言道，一路上有两座"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凶山难过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一心想摘天边月，只恨足下不生云。男儿不遇空抱恨"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时运不至当快手"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪两座？这一？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金顶太行山"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "铁角束阻山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "出的什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惯出响马贼寇，打劫来往客商。彼时皇甫大人要保镖护送。我家太爷，回得衙"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来打鼓升堂，点了二十名人役。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可在内？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人也在其内，保定皇甫大人过了金顶太行山安然无事。来在铁角束阻山，耳"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "边只听哗啦哗啦，人马呐喊。小人抬头一看，只见半山有旗，旗上写得分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上写什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上写混天大王，惯打来往客商，过路官员。彼时皇甫大人，下了驼轿，扫地一"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "躬，口称历城县的好汉弟兄，哪一个保我举家过得此山安然无事，有如重生父"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母，再世爹娘，恩有重报，义不敢忘。只见众人役一个一个低头不语。那时小"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人走上前去，双膝跪下。口称大人在上，小人有心保定大人举家无事；手中虽"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有兵刃，坐下无有马匹。彼时皇甫大人在驼轿之后牵出一匹马来，那马项上有"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "牌，牌上有字。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上写什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上写“此马似黄骠，四蹄无杂毛，好似南山豹，如同浪里蛟。”千岁！好啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一匹黄骠马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄骠马儿世间稀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四蹄一纵如云飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要与强贼比高低。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人与那贼战了数十余合，不分胜败。小人心生一计，圈马就走。那贼不解其"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "意，催马赶上。小人回头一看，马头相连马尾；撒手一锏，实指望将他打死；"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不料他乃行伍出身，滚鞍法滚下马来，双手抱住锏头。口称好汉身为天下英雄，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何不锏下留情？俺与他无冤无仇，岂肯伤他性命。将锏高高举起，轻轻落下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他解开其意，催马就走。小人一见加鞭赶上。呀呔，山贼好生无礼，俺锏下"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "留情，饶你性命。谢字不答，名姓不通，是何理也？那人通上名来！乃河北渑"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "池县人氏，姓单名通字雄信，说来说去，这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一马儿来在山凹里"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八拜为交。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既为英雄，与强盗结交也就不高了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁！小人当了差役，此等人不得不交。他被小人相劝，如今不当响马了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "作什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在天堂潞州开了一座马场，小人时常来往，多亏此人周济。保定皇甫大人天堂"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荣任，无以为谢，愿将此马为赠，以为终身之报也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇甫爷路过束阻山，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦琼单人保家眷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "锏打雄信拜马前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就是小战场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高高举起劈棱锏"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将小战场压下，大战场讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启千岁：那年历城县出了一十八名江洋大盗，我家太爷，命小人原拿原解，解"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "往潞州，在兵部大堂挂号了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵部大堂挂号文，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离了西地美良城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄骠马不走发嘶声！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁，小人到了……"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一马儿来至在临潼郡"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到了何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "临潼山！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么，你也到过临潼山？本藩最喜的临潼山。讲来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人行至临潼山，天气炎热，牵马下涧饮水，只见二怪争斗："
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦琼离山东，风俗大不同。山东龙戏珠，山西珠戏龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手执顽石往下打，只见二怪腾了空。满满搭上朱红扣，箭射红珠救青龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦琼生来力猛勇，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两膀能开百石弓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "箭射红珠救青龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人射了红珠一箭，助了青龙一膀之力。耳边又听哗啦啦，人马呐喊，小人站"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "立高坡一看，见一黄袍将官，与一绿袍将官交战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满满搭上朱红扣"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绿袍将官他是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个小人不敢讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却是为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与千岁重名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天下重名甚多。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也是庆国公李渊、李千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那黄袍的将官？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何不讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳目甚重。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左右退下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讲来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是东宫太子杨广。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他君臣因何交战？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因李千岁，大下江南一十一载，得胜回朝，文帝老王摆宴，与李千岁庆功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨广、宇文化及陪宴。酒席筵前提起谋朝篡位，怒恼李千岁，手执紫金杯，隔"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "席打去。只望打死宇文化及，不料失手打落奸王门牙。李千岁心中害怕，连夜"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辞表，告职归里。千岁想，那奸王打牙仇恨，难道说罢了不成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是呀！后来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨广在他父王前面，讨下精兵，行围射猎。哪里是行围射猎，分明兵扎临潼山，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "捉拿李千岁满门家眷。只杀得李千岁披头散发，甲叶乱飞。小人一见，打了"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "个抱不平。谁料败下阵来，小人抬头一看，只见半山有杆，杆上有斗，斗内有"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人。手内执旗，旗往东倒，人马东杀；旗往西倒，人马西杀。那旗何日得倒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人马何日得散。小人黄骠马有纵山之力，人借马力，马借人力，纵上山去，将"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旗打倒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦琼生来世无比，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两膀生就千斤力。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金锏打倒杏黄旗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人将旗打倒，人马散去大半。奸王与小人交战，战了数十回合，不分胜败。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人催马败走，奸王加鞭赶上。马头相连马尾，小人撒手一锏，直说将奸王打"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "死；不料他有一朝大王之分，打伤左膀，败进关去。东门上锁，西门上闩，捉"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿李千岁满门家眷，捎带小人。自古道杀人……"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一马闯上山坡里"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "救人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "救活！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着，着，着！小人将关门打开，也不知放走多少客商行人。李千岁满门家眷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也混过关去，小人一见加鞭赶上。呀呔！你这败将好生无礼也，想俺在两军阵"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上，舍死忘生救了你全家性命，谢也不答，名姓不通，是何道理？彼时李千岁，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "通名上来，俺庆国公李渊，来谢恩公，不知贵姓高名？那时小人本当说出真"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "名实姓，怎奈，关前关后俱是奸王耳目。想小人锏上原有“秦琼”二字，小人"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "按住“秦”字，露出“琼”字，将军请看。李千岁言道，敢是“琼”？小人把"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手一摆，他言道原来“琼五”大将军。本藩回至太原，恩有重报，义不敢当。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人只是救了李千岁之后，奔波劳碌，直到如今也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三大二小共一秦，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "临潼山下解配军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双锏黄骠作证凭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁如若不肯信"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "锏、马现在何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在帐外。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "取来我看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听说一声要锏、马，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒把秦琼活吓杀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要劈棱犹如同把膀臂拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不由人回转身仔细盘查。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要黄骠似将我双足剁下"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无奈何我只得宝帐来下"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还不下去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这千岁在哪里会过大驾？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一时想他不起！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫非是临潼山救的是他？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是他是他真是他！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不该大帐盘问咱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "生死二字怕甚么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "劈棱双锏手中拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就是救驾的锏共马；二九一十八一点也不差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大丈夫生在三光下"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用手儿带过黄骠马"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走上前来忙跪下"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本藩下位观黄骠，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回身又观锏二条。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "举家大小把香烧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不料相会在今朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为你盖下琼五庙"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只说恩人亡故了"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走上前来忙跪倒"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人不敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本是庆国公李渊两保隋朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庆国公李渊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你，庆国公李千岁？"
        }
